---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer>
    <div class="footer-container">
        <div class="footer-section company-info">
            <h3>T-Vetas Network</h3>
            <p>致力於成為台灣最可靠的基礎建設服務商</p>
            <p>114 台北市內湖區堤頂大道二段283號3樓</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-section contact">
            <h3>聯絡資訊</h3>
            <p>業務諮詢：Alpha</p>
            <p>電話：0910-663118</p>
            <p>Email：alpha@vetastech.com</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-section service-hours">
            <h3>服務時間</h3>
            <p>週一至週五</p>
            <p>09:00 - 18:00</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-bottom">
        <p>&copy; {today.getFullYear()} T-Vetas Network. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</footer>

<style>
    footer {
        background: #1A2A47;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }

    .footer-container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .footer-section {
        padding: 1rem;
    }

    .footer-section h3 {
        color: #FF7A00;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .footer-section p {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        color: #f5f7fa;
    }

    .footer-bottom {
        text-align: center;
        padding-top: 2rem;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .footer-container {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            text-align: center;
        }
    }
</style>
